# Geocoder backends.
#
# Search runs through Photon (autocomplete-grade prefix matching) and
# boundary retrieval runs through Nominatim (relation -> polygon). All four
# variables are OPTIONAL — the backend ships with working defaults pointing
# at the public instances. Override these to point at self-hosted services
# or to set a User-Agent that complies with each provider's usage policy
# (a descriptive identifier with a contact email).
#
# NOMINATIM_BASE_URL=https://nominatim.openstreetmap.org
# NOMINATIM_USER_AGENT=thermotree/0.1 (contact: you@example.com)
# PHOTON_BASE_URL=https://photon.komoot.io
# PHOTON_USER_AGENT=thermotree/0.1 (contact: you@example.com)

# STAC backends, in priority order. Comma-separated. The first reachable
# backend wins; subsequent backends are tried only on network/HTTP errors
# (timeouts, 5xx, connection failures). A 0-items result or a quality
# rejection from the primary is treated as authoritative and does NOT
# trigger fallback. Valid names: planetary_computer, element84.
#
# STAC_PROVIDERS=planetary_computer,element84
